2007;;Dr. Plonk;;Australian;;Rolf de Heer;;Nigel Lunghi, Magda Szubanski;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dr_Plonk;;The story focuses on Dr Plonk, a scientist and inventor who, in 1907, determines that the world will end in 101 years. However, he is ridiculed for his beliefs and so invents a time machine in order to collect evidence from the future to prove his case. But each visit he makes to 2007 only causes him more problems, and he eventually becomes a wanted man...